| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0148 — Recovery Inhibition (kairos)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9e7488bc-7dc4-55ed-8c80-b6b4ec2f4fff"
